<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="Resume/CV of Alexander Hinds">
  <title>Resume</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" type="text/css" />
</head>

<body>
  <header class="container">
    <img src="/logo.svg" />
    <h1>Alex Hinds</h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="column">
      <div class="container left-column">
        <section class="bio">
          <h2 class="section-header">About</h2>
          <p>I'm a software engineer and former journalist with a passion for UX/UI, frontend
            engineering
            and web development.</p>
          <p>
            I bring a unique set of skills and experience with nearly a decade in journalism,
            combined with a solid technical grounding
            in computer science.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="bio">
          <h2 class="section-header">Education</h2>
          {{#each qualifications}}
          <article>
            <h3>{{this.course}}</h3>
            <p>{{this.provider}}, {{this.graduation_year}}, {{this.majors}}.</p>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
        </section>
        <section class="bio">
          <h2 class="section-header">Technical Skills</h2>
          <article id="code">
            <p>
              I'm comfortable working in C, Java, JavaScript (Full Stack), Python, HTML and
              CSS. I've worked largely in a Unix/Linux environment,
              and have worked with React, Vue.js, React Native, Flask, Django, Express.js,
              and dabbled
              with other frameworks.
            </p>
            <p>For a more complete overview, please check out my <a href="https://github.com/DarkPurple141">Github</a>
              or my <a href="https://alhinds.com">personal
                website.</a></p>
          </article>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="column">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-header">Experience</h2>
        <section>
          {{#each jobs}}
          <article class="job">
            <h3><a href="{{this.href}}">{{this.company}}</a>, {{this.title}}, {{this.start_date}}-{{this.end_date}}</h3>
            <p>{{this.description}}</p>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
          <article class="job">
            <h3>Other notables</h3>
            <p>I'm an occassional OSS contributor, I've co-authored a book on the Tour de
              France,
              and have appeared on ABC radio, triple j.</p>
          </article>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="container">
    <p class="footer-link">Phone. <a href="tel:+61411849217">+61 411 849 217</a></p>
    <p class="footer-link">Email. <a href="mailto:alex.hinds141@gmail.com">alex.hinds141@gmail.com</a></p>
    <p class="footer-link">Website. <a href="https://alhinds.com">alhinds.com</a></p>
    <p class="footer-link">Github. <a href="https://github.com/DarkPurple141">@DarkPurple141</a></p>
    <p class="footer-link">Linkedin. <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-hinds-12449660/">Alex Hinds</a>
    </p>
    <p class="footer-link">Medium. <a href="https://medium.com/@al_hinds">@al_hinds</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
